
Player Commands

--- Register ---
curl -X POST localhost:3000/newuser -d 'username,password'

--- IPScanner ---
curl -X GET localhost:3000/ipscanner.exe -d 'username,password,keyword'

--- ShowStats ---
curl -X GET localhost:3000/statuscenter.exe -d 'username,password'

--- Reset IP ---
curl -X PUT localhost:3000/hide-me.exe -d 'username,password'

--- Heal ---
curl X- PUT localhost:3000/updatefirewall.exe -d 'username,password'

--- Attack ---
curl -X PUT localhost:3000/attack/insertIPaddress -d 'username,password'

--- Auto Decrypt ---
curl -X GET localhost:3000/autodecrypt/insertIPaddress/insertKeyword -d 'username,password'

--- Final Hack ---
curl -X PUT localhost:3000/finalhack/insertdummypassword/inserttargetIP -d 'username,password'
